<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نَسِيمُهَا تَفُوحُ مِنهُ السِّيرَةُ المُعَطَّرَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَأَهْلُهَا وُجُوهُهُمْ * بَشُوشَةٌ وَمُقْمِرَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نُفُوسُهُمْ نَقِيَّةٌ * تَقِيَّةٌ وَخَيِّرَة<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَيْسَتْ طِبَاعُهُمْ غَلِيظَةً وَلاَ مُنَفِّرَة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>*<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِنْ كُنْتُ لَمْ أَزُرْكِ قَطُّ مَرَّةً فَمَعْذِرَة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>دَوْمَاً بِمِصْرَ حَالَةُ الأَدِيبِ غَيرُ مُوسِرَة<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لِذَا اكْتَفَيْتُ أَن أَرَاكِ في الرُّؤَى المُبَشِّرَة<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>*<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَمَكَّةُ المُكَرَّمَة * مَدِينَةٌ مُعَظَّمَة<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَمَدْحُهَا يُحِبُّ كُلُّ شَاعِرٍ أَنْ يَنْظِمَه<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قُلُوبُنَا بِحُبِّهَا * مَلِيئَةٌ وَمُفْعَمَة<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَحَوْلَ بَيْتِهَا الحَرَامِ رُوحُنَا مُحَوِّمَة<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>اللهُمَّ عَلَيْكَ بِالْيَهُود<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>إِذَا مَا بحَثْتَ بِهَذَا الْوُجُودْ * عَنِ الشَّرِّ كَانَ بِفِعْلِ الْيَهُودْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>خِدَاعٌ وَمَطْلٌ وَقَتْلٌ وَبَطْشٌ * وَغِشٌّ وَغَدْرٌ بِكُلِّ الْعُهُودْ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>